Package model

Class Tableau

java.lang.Object
model.Tableau
public class Tableau
extends java.lang.Object
The class Tableau represents a tableau used in a solitaire game. It provides access to the card columns used and ways to access the images used in the cards.
Version:
2020.11.17
Author:
Devon X. Dalrymple
